TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT B.ACCOUNT + ' ' + B.SUB_ACCOUNT AS LAW_CAT_CODE_DESC, LTRIM(RTRIM(STR(A.COMPANY))) as COMPANY_CODE, ISNULL(A.AMOUNT_ESS,0) as LAWSON_DOLLARS, A.FISCAL_YEAR as FISCAL_YEAR, A.PERIOD as FISCAL_PERIOD, LTRIM(RTRIM(A.ORG_KEY)) as ORG_KEY FROM DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS as A WITH(NOLOCK), DW_GL_ACCOUNT as B WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE A.ACCT_KEY = B.ACCT_KEY AND A.FISCAL_YEAR = $$YEAR AND A.PERIOD = $$MONTH_NUM AND A.CURRENCY_TYPE = 'BASE' AND A.COMPANY_GROUP = 'SLD-INCDIMX' AND A.SCENARIO = 'ACTUAL' --GROUP BY --B.ACCOUNT + ' ' + B.SUB_ACCOUNT , --A.COMPANY, --A.FISCAL_YEAR, --A.PERIOD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on gross margin to get the data
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_GROSS_MARGIN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT R.CHAIN_ACCOUNT AS CHAIN_ACCOUNT , NVL(R.CATEGORY_DESC,'--') AS CATEGORY_DESC , SUM(NVL(R.CALC_SALES,0)) AS SALES_AMT , SUM(NVL(R.CALC_COST,0)) AS COST_AMT , FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR , FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD FROM ( SELECT A.CHAIN_ACCOUNT_DESC AS CHAIN_ACCOUNT , case when B.UPDATE_USERID='DTC BI Outlet GM' then case when B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME='Allow' then 'Gross OS' when B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME='Disc' then 'Gross OS' else B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME end else B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME end as CATEGORY_DESC -- , B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME AS CATEGORY_DESC , SUM(NVL(B.DOLLARS,0) ) AS CALC_SALES , 0 AS CALC_COST , B.FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR , B.FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD FROM GROSS_MARGIN B , XRF_ACC A WHERE B.SLBA_DIVISION_CODE = 'DR' AND A.TS_DIV_CDE = 'DR' AND B.SOURCE_ACCOUNT_NUM = A.SOLDTO AND B.FISCAL_YEAR = $$YEAR AND B.FISCAL_PERIOD = $$MONTH_NUM AND B.GROSS_MARGIN_IND='Y' GROUP BY A.CHAIN_ACCOUNT_DESC -- , B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME , case when B.UPDATE_USERID='DTC BI Outlet GM' then case when B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME='Allow' then 'Gross OS' when B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME='Disc' then 'Gross OS' else B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME end else B.SALES_MEASURE_NAME end , B.FISCAL_YEAR , B.FISCAL_PERIOD UNION ALL SELECT A.CHAIN_ACCOUNT_DESC AS CHAIN_ACCOUNT , B.COST_MEASURE_NAME AS CATEGORY_DESC , 0 AS CALC_SALES , SUM(NVL(B.ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS,0)) AS CALC_COST , B.FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR , B.FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD FROM GROSS_MARGIN B , XRF_ACC A WHERE B.SLBA_DIVISION_CODE = 'DR' AND A.TS_DIV_CDE = 'DR' AND B.SOURCE_ACCOUNT_NUM = A.SOLDTO AND B.FISCAL_YEAR = $$YEAR AND B.FISCAL_PERIOD = $$MONTH_NUM AND B.GROSS_MARGIN_IND='Y' GROUP BY A.CHAIN_ACCOUNT_DESC , B.COST_MEASURE_NAME , B.FISCAL_YEAR , B.FISCAL_PERIOD ) R GROUP BY R.CHAIN_ACCOUNT , NVL(R.CATEGORY_DESC, '--') , R.FISCAL_YEAR , R.FISCAL_PERIOD

SESSION.DESCRIPTION: Session to load history data for DTC in Gross Margin from Lawson
SESSION.NAME: s_m_GM_DR_LAWSON_CUR_YR

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
update gross_margin g set py_dollars =dollars ,py_adj_extended_cost_dollars = adj_extended_cost_dollars where g.fiscal_year = (select case when to_number(d.cy_month_num) !=12 then to_number(d.cy_year_yyyy) else to_number(d.cy_year_yyyy)-1 end from slba.day_dimension d where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) and g.fiscal_period= (select case when to_number(d.cy_month_num) !=12 then to_number(d.cy_month_num)-1 else 12 end from slba.day_dimension d where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) and g.gross_margin_ind='Y' and g.slba_division_code in ('DR') ; commit;
update ( select g.fiscal_year , g.fiscal_period, g.py_dollars, g.py_adj_extended_cost_dollars, case when invoiced_quality_code ='1' or invoiced_quality_code ='6' and upper(i.level_1_name) != 'FINANCE' then decode(g.sales_measure_name,'Gross OS', decode(sign(nvl(avg_price_dollars,0)),0,dollars,g.garments*avg_price_dollars),dollars) else dollars end recast_dollars, case when invoiced_quality_code ='1' or invoiced_quality_code ='6' and upper(i.level_1_name) != 'FINANCE' then decode(cost_measure_name,'OS COGS', decode(sign(nvl(avg_cost_dollars,0)),0,adj_extended_cost_dollars,g.garments*avg_cost_dollars),adj_extended_cost_dollars) else adj_extended_cost_dollars end recast_cost from slba.gross_margin g join slba.slba_item i ON i.item_id = g.item_id join slba.Average_Cost_Price_by_Item a on g.item_id =a.item_id and g.fiscal_year=a.fiscal_year and g.fiscal_period=a.fiscal_period where g.fiscal_year = (select case when to_number(d.cy_month_num) !=12 then to_number(d.cy_year_yyyy) else to_number(d.cy_year_yyyy)-1 end from slba.day_dimension d where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) and g.fiscal_period= (select case when to_number(d.cy_month_num) !=12 then to_number(d.cy_month_num)-1 else 12 end from slba.day_dimension d where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) and g.gross_margin_ind='Y' and (g.sales_measure_name='Gross OS' or g.cost_measure_name='OS COGS') --and g.ppk_indicator!='Y' and g.slba_division_code in ('DR') ) set py_dollars =recast_dollars ,py_adj_extended_cost_dollars = recast_cost ; commit;
